Package skywaysolutions.app.database

package skywaysolutions.app.database
This package provides database access.
  • Class
    Description
    DatabaseBackupTable
    This class represents a backup of a database table.
    DatabaseEntityBase
    This class provides a base class that is used by all database stored entities.
    DatabaseTableBase<T extends DatabaseEntityBase>
    This class provides a base class that is used by all database table managers.
    DB_Connector
    This class provides a MySQL IDB_Connector implementation.
    IDB_Connector
    Provides an Interface for using a database connection.
    IFilterStatementCreator
    This interface provides the ability for DatabaseTableBase.loadMany(IFilterStatementCreator, MultiLoadSyncMode) to have custom filters.
    MultiLoadSyncMode
    This enum provides the loading modes for multi load support in DatabaseTableBase.
